	-------------  Angular_with_Cordova --------------------------------
	
		Npm install -g cordova
		Cardova create cordova_app
		Cordova platform add browser 
		Cordova platform add browser 
		Cordova run browser 
		 Step for environment variable :  - ANDROID_HOME
		C:\Users\Optebiz\AppData\Local\Android\Sdk
		Add in Path of Environment Variable : - C:\Users\Optebiz\AppData\Local\Android\Sdk\platforms
		C:\Users\Optebiz\AppData\Local\Android\Sdk\platform-tools

